Created entirely in c++ and includes 3 steps: 

Quizzes:
        Engage in quizzes spanning various difficulty levels to test and solidify your understanding of musical notes and chords.

Lessons:
        Explore structured guitar lessons that offer a systematic approach to learning fundamental concepts, including chords.

SFML-Powered Game:
                  Interactive game environment, skillfully implemented using SFML. Play notes within the game. 
